======================================================================
ANALYSIS 1: THE 2D H-MANIFOLD
======================================================================

n=5: H-manifold analysis
  Total tournaments: 1024
  (var_s, H_4) determines H uniquely? True
  Number of (var_s, H_4) pairs: 8
  Number of distinct H values: 7
  H is a FUNCTION of (score_variance, H_4) -- confirmed!
  The H-manifold is EXACTLY 2-dimensional.

  Score variance | #H4 values | H4 range
  ---------------+------------+---------
           0.0000 |          1 | 0.0
           0.4000 |          3 | -1.0 to 3.0
           0.8000 |          1 | 0.0
           1.2000 |          1 | -1.0
           1.6000 |          1 | 0.0
           2.0000 |          1 | 1.0

n=6: H-manifold analysis
